casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Ronald Dale MICHAEL.
No. D-2887.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 16, 2016.
Ronald Dale Michael, of Booneville, Mississippi, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
